# Build context for the repo-root build (Dockerfile-db) only needs db/.
# Exclude everything heavy/irrelevant so that context stays tiny. Per-service
# image builds use their own context (src/<svc>) + their own .dockerignore.
.git
.github
.idea
**/.DS_Store
src/
proto/
web/
*.md
docker-compose*.yml

# Build artifacts / caches (belt-and-suspenders for any future root builds)
**/target/
**/build/
**/.gradle/
**/node_modules/
**/__pycache__/
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
